column5: John have Wayne raise the door frame about 6 inches on the ice shack for me,it won't bother the wife she's only 5ft1.thanks n goodnight.
For you guys travelling north from Vermilion Bay this is the Buller Creek you bounce over.
New truck had a lot of mud underneath so it got a good wash both ways.
What truck you driving now john?
I'd probably hit that water going about 80 and wash my truck and any truck behind me or coming the other way.
2022 f150 xtr.Hit it pretty good after I took pic.Water came up on windshield lol.it will rise more yet.Happens every year
Yup that's a new truck,it will haul those freebie minnows around nicely,and your boat,by not having to pay for minnows you saved enough to buy that truck.
Great being on a free minnow ride just like all of clarks guests.lol.Probably minnow prices are going to go up along with everything else.
So do you think you'll be paying maybe a penny a minnow??or you still gonna be on a help yourself minnow buffet?
Gee let me think on that. Nope think ill stick with the help myself deal.
